      "content": "# User Profile Retrieval Endpoint (`GET /user`)\n\n## Overview\nThis endpoint allows authenticated users to retrieve their personal profile data. It serves as the primary mechanism for fetching essential user identification details.\n\n### Request Details\n#### Endpoint Path\n`/user`\n\n#### HTTP Method\n`GET`\n\n### Response Structure\n#### Success Response (200 OK)\nThe response body will contain a JSON object detailing the user's profile.\n\n##### Data Fields\n*   `id`: Unique identifier for the user.\n*   `name`: The full display name of the user.\n*   `email`: The primary email address associated with the account.\n\n#### Error Responses\nDetails regarding potential errors, such as 401 Unauthorized, will be provided in the response body for debugging purposes.",
